end / License / BreadcrumbLicense'=>'Licencja','Backend / Service Location / LabelPath'=>'Ścieżka','Backend / License / Button TitleRefresh License Information'=>'Odśwież informacje o licencji','Backend / Service Location / Headline<translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Locations">Adresy</translation-key>','Backend / License / Button TitleRemove License'=>'Usuń licencję','Backend / Service Location / Table HeadlineHostname'=>'Nazwa hosta','Backend / License / LabelCloud Scans'=>'Skanowania w chmurze','Backend / Service Location / Table HeadlinePath'=>'Ścieżka','Backend / License / LabelConfirm Refresh'=>'Potwierdź odświeżenie','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is a <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>?'=>'Co to jest <translation-key id="Hostname">Nazwa hosta</translation-key>?','Backend / License / LabelLicense Key'=>'Klucz licencyjny','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key> section?'=>'Do czego służy obszar <translation-key id="Locations">Adresy</translation-key>?','Backend / License / LabelLicense Name'=>'Nazwa licencji','Backend / Service Location / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is the domain name of the website. For example, if the URL of the website is <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, the <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'<translation-key id="Hostname">Nazwa hosta</translation-key> to nazwa domeny witryny internetowej. Jeżeli na przykład adres URL strony internetowej to <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, wtedy <translation-key id="Hostname">Nazwa hosta</translation-key> to <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / License / LabelLicense Status'=>'Status licencji','Backend / Service Loca